<h2><span class="mw-headline" id="Match_officials">Match officials</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=1997_Copa_Am%C3%A9rica&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3" title="Edit section: Match officials"><span>edit</span></a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h2>
