<h3><span class="mw-headline" id="Ranking_of_third-placed_teams">Ranking of third-placed teams</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=1997_Copa_Am%C3%A9rica&amp;action=edit&amp;section=8" title="Edit section: Ranking of third-placed teams"><span>edit</span></a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h3>
<p>At the end of the first stage, a comparison was made between the third-placed teams of each group. The two best third-placed teams advanced to the quarter-finals.
</p>

